The '''2019 [[ICF World Junior and U23 Canoe Slalom Championships]]''' will take place in [[Rio de Janeiro]], [[Brazil]] from 1 to 5 May 2019 under the auspices of the [[International Canoe Federation]] (ICF) at the [[Deodoro Olympic Whitewater Stadium]].<ref>{{cite web|title=2019 ICF CANOE SLALOM JUNIOR & U23 WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP (DATES TBC)|url=https://www.canoeicf.com/canoe-slalom-world-championships/rio-de-janeiro-2019|website=CanoeICF.com|accessdate=23 February 2018}}</ref> It will be the 21st edition of the competition for Juniors (U18) and the 8th edition for the Under 23 category.
