== Mascot == Kon, the Con-G mascot, was a cartoon [[Japanese dragon]]. He was green with a white belly and a purple mane, and was often depicted holding a [[calligraphy]] brush. He was created for Con-G by artist Lindsay Pattillo.<ref>{{cite web | url = http://con-g.com/information/staff/ | title = Con-G 2012 Staff | publisher = Con-G.com | accessdate = March 14, 2012}}</ref>
